name: array_diff_uassoc
purpose: Computes the difference of arrays with additional index check which is performed by a user supplied callback function

return.description:
Returns an array containing all the entries from
   array1 that are not present in any of the other arrays.

notes.description:
This function only checks one dimension of a n-dimensional
    array. Of course you can check deeper dimensions by using, for example,
    array_diff_uassoc($array1[0], $array2[0], "key_compare_func");.
